OL,3,CTfL open consultation into pedicabs
OL,4,Cfollowing 'rip off fares'
OL,6,FTransport for London is inviting
OL,7,Fpeople to have their say on pedicabs
OL,8,Fin the capital for the first time.
OL,10,FThey are the only form of unregulated
OL,11,Fpublic transport in the city, and the
OL,12,Fplans hope to make them as safe a
OL,13,Fpossible whilst tackling the issue of
OL,14,F'rip off fares'.
