OL,3,CTfL open consultation into pedicabs
OL,4,Cfollowing 'rip off fares'
OL,6,FWill Norman, the Walking and Cycling
OL,7,FCommissioner said: "Pedicabs should be
OL,8,Fa fun and sustainable way for people
OL,9,Fto see London but, without regulation,
OL,10,Fsome drivers are behaving unsafely or
OL,11,Fantisocially, and charging
OL,12,Fextortionate prices.
OL,14,F"I'm pleased that TfL are launching
OL,15,Fthis consultation on how to regulate
OL,16,Fthe pedicab industry, ensuring the
OL,17,Fsafety of customers, pedestrians and
OL,18,Fother road users."
OL,20,FTfL is seeking views on the following
OL,21,Fproposals:
