OL,3,CTfL open consultation into pedicabs
OL,4,Cfollowing 'rip off fares'
OL,6,FThese new regulations would bring
OL,7,Fpedicabs up to the same standards as
OL,8,Fother taxis.
OL,10,FHelen Chapman, TfL's Director of
OL,11,FLicensing & Regulation, said:
OL,12,F"Pedicabs are the only form of
OL,13,Funregulated public transport in London
OL,14,Fand have an impact on the safety of
OL,15,Fthe capital's road network, as well as
OL,16,Fcustomers being charged well-
OL,17,Fdocumented rip-off fares, so we're
OL,18,Fpleased to be able to launch this
OL,19,Fconsultation.
