OL,3,CTfL open consultation into pedicabs
OL,4,Cfollowing 'rip off fares'
OL,6,F"I'd encourage everyone to take part
OL,7,Fin our consultation and to have their
OL,8,Fsay as people's feedback will be vital
OL,9,Fto ensuring the changes work for
OL,10,Feveryone. We're looking forward to
OL,11,Fworking with the pedicab industry, to
OL,12,Fensure it is run safely and fairly."
OL,14,FCurrently there is no consistency in
OL,15,Fthe fares but this could change with
OL,16,Fthe introduction of time-based,
OL,17,Fdistance-based, or zonal structure.
