OL,6,FThe pedicabs also play loud music but
OL,7,F'antisocial' behaviour and noise
OL,8,Foffences are already covered by
OL,9,Fexisting legislation though TfL may
OL,10,Fintroduce restrictions on noise levels
OL,11,Fparticularly at certain times of day.
OL,13,FTfL also say this would only apply to
OL,14,F"pedicabs carrying paying passengers
OL,15,Fand 'party bikes'" and that "vehicles
OL,16,Fwhich are used to carry freight, other
OL,17,Fnon-passenger carrying services, and
OL,18,Fthose for personal use will not be
OL,19,Fcovered by regulations from this
OL,20,Fconsultation".
